#. Tag: title
#: mount.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "MountMan: work with your mounted file systems"
msgstr "MountMan: radite sa svojim montiranim fajl sistemima"

#. Tag: primary
#: mount.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount"
msgstr "Montiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:12
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "MountMan is a tool which helps you manage your mounted file systems. Once "
#| "invoked, it displays a list of every mounted file system. For each file "
#| "system, MountMan displays its name (which is the actual device name - "
#| "&ie; <filename class=\"directory\">/dev/sda1</filename> for a first "
#| "partition on first <hardware>HDD</hardware>), its type (ext4, ext3, ntfs, "
#| "vfat, ReiserFS...) and its mount point on your system (the directory on "
#| "which the file system is mounted)."
msgid ""
"MountMan is a tool which helps you manage your mounted file systems. Once "
"invoked, it displays a list of every mounted file system. For each file "
"system, MountMan displays its name (which is the actual device name - &ie; "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/dev/sda1</filename> for a first partition on "
"first <hardware>HDD</hardware>), its type (ext4, ext3, ntfs, vfat, "
"ReiserFS...) and its mount point on your system (the folder on which the "
"file system is mounted)."
msgstr ""
"MountMan je alat koji vam pomaže da upravljate svojim montiranim fajlovima. "
"Kada se poziva, prikazuje listu svih montiranih fajl sistema.  Za svaki fajl "
"sistem, MountMan prikazuje ime (što je stvarni naziv uređaja - &ie; "
"<filename class=\"directory\"> / Dev / sda1 </filename> za prvu particiju na "
"prvom <hardware> HDD </hardware> ),njegov tip  (ext4, ext3, ntfs, vfat, "
"ReiserFS...) i njegove tačku na vašem sistemu (direktorij na koji se montira "
"fajl sistem)."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want filter out non-removable devices from the list, just check the "
"item <guilabel>Show only removable devices</guilabel> at the left of the "
"device list."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite filtrirati neizbrisive uređaje s popisa, samo provjerite stavku "
"<guilabel> Pokaži samo prenosive uređaji </guilabel> na lijevoj strani liste "
"uređaja."

#. Tag: title
#: mount.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>MountMan</title>"
msgstr "<title> MountMan </title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: mount.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>MountMan</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase> MountMan </phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"MountMan also displays usage information using total size, free size, and "
"percentage of available space free. If those numbers say <guilabel>N/A</"
"guilabel>, that usually means that the file system is not mounted. Left "
"clicking on a file system displays a pie chart on the left of the window, "
"graphically displaying the usage information for the file system. Clicking "
"on a non-mounted file system will display <guilabel>not mounted</guilabel> "
"instead of the graph."
msgstr ""
"MountMan  također pokazuje upotrebu informacija korištenjem ukupnog "
"prostora, slobodnog prostora i procentom dostupnog prostora. Ako ti brojevi "
"kažu <guilabel>N/A</guilabel>, to obićno znači da fajl sistem nije montiran. "
"Lijevim klikom na fajl sistem vidjećete tabelu na lijevoj strani prozora, "
"koja grafički prokazuje upotrebu informacija za fajl sistem. klikom na "
"nemontirani fajl sistem vidjećete <guilabel> nemontiran </guilabel> umjesto "
"grafa."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Double-clicking</keycap> on a file system will close MountMan and "
"open that file system inside &krusader;'s active panel."
msgstr ""
"<keycap> Dupli klik </keycap> na fajl sistem će se zatvoriti MountMan/a i "
"otvoriti taj fajl sistem unutar &krusader;-ovog aktivnog panela."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>Right-clicking</keycap> on a file system will open a small menu "
"which displays what actions can be performed on that file system. At the "
"moment, you can only mount, unmount and eject (if clicking on a removable "
"file system, &eg;, a &CD-ROM;)."
msgstr ""
"<keycap> Desnim klikom </keycap> na fajl sistem će se otvoriti mali izbornik "
"koji prikazuje koje akcije možete izvršiti na tom fajl sistem. U trenutku, "
"možete samo montirati, demontirati i izbacite (ako kliknete na prenosivi "
"fajl sistem,&eg;, a &CD-ROM;)."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:60
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "We plan to expand MountMan in the next evolution of &krusader;. It will "
#| "be able to format partitions, edit <filename>/etc/fstab</filename>, "
#| "create new file systems and more.... By the way, we have started working "
#| "on it, see \"Quickmode for MountMan\"."
msgid ""
"We plan to expand MountMan in the next evolution of &krusader;. It will be "
"able to format partitions, edit <filename>/etc/fstab</filename>, create new "
"file systems and more.... By the way, we have started working on it, see "
"<quote>Quickmode for MountMan</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Planiramo da proširimo MountMan u naredni stepen &krusader;. Moći će da "
"formatira particije, uređuje <filename>/etc/fstab</filename>, stvara nove "
"fajl sisteme i još više.... Usput,počeli smo da radimo na njemu, pogledajte "
"\"Brzi režim MountMan\"."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: mount.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quickmode for MountMan"
msgstr "Brza verzija za MountMan-a"

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To activate Quickmode for MountMan, click lateral button with arrow on the "
"MountMan button on the <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main Toolbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Da biste aktivirali brzi režim MountMan-a, kliknite na tipku sa strane sa "
"strelicom na MountMan tipki na <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Glavna Alatna "
"traka</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: mount.docbook:70
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "General idea: display a list of all possible mount points. Each time the "
#| "menu is displayed, it determines if a mount point is mounted or not and "
#| "associates the correct action (mount or umount). This offers a quick "
#| "interface to MountMan. It is working, and currently uses KMountMan::mount "
#| "and unmount. It uses the new &kde; services for fstab-reading and this "
#| "will enable us to remove a lot of code from the \"old\" MountMan."
msgid ""
"General idea: display a list of all possible mount points. Each time the "
"menu is displayed, it determines if a mount point is mounted or not and "
"associates the correct action (mount or umount). This offers a quick "
"interface to MountMan. It is working, and currently uses KMountMan::mount "
"and unmount. It uses the new &kf5-full; services for fstab-reading and this "
"will enable us to remove a lot of code from the <quote>old</quote> MountMan."
msgstr ""
"Uopštena ideja: prikaži listu svih mogućih tački montiranja. Svaki put kada "
"je izbornik prikazan, određuje da li je montirana tačka namontirana ili ne i "
"povezuje sa tačnom radnjom (montirati ili odmontirati). Ovo nudi brzo "
"povezivanje sa MountMan-om. Radi i trenutno koristi KMountMan::montirati i "
"odmontirati.  Koristi nove &kde; usluge, usluge za fstab čitanje i ovo će "
"nam omogućiti da uklonimo mnogo kodova iz  \"old\" MountMan-a."
